N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 30.6 - Fees

State Regulations

The registration fee for a vehicle in a fleet shall be the
same as that for a vehicle not in a fleet except that there shall be an annual
$2 per vehicle administrative fee for fleet vehicles. Notes
